&lt;strong&gt;Output&lt;/strong&gt;: &amp;quot;e&amp;quot;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Explanation&lt;/strong&gt;: &#39;e&#39; is the letter that was added.&lt;/p&gt;
