&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NOTAPALINDROME -- is not a palindrome.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;ISAPALINILAPASI -- is a regular palindrome.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;2A3MEAS -- is a mirrored string.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;ATOYOTA -- is a mirrored palindrome.&lt;/p&gt;
